## Memory & mechanisms

- `.ai_context/` is this project's persistent memory. `INDEX.md` + `state.md`
  are injected automatically at session start (`.claude/settings.json`
  hooks), including after compaction — no manual protocol needed.
- Run `/wrap` at the end of a session to write memory back.
- For instant lint feedback on every edit, copy
  `.claude/hooks/lint.sh.example` → `lint.sh` once the stack exists.
